<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Student Hubs</title>
    <%- include('partials/header.ejs') %>
    <%- include('partials/navbar1.ejs') %>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: white;
        }
        .container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 30px;
            background-color: white;
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 40px auto;
        }
        .container2 {
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: white;
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 50px auto;
        }
        .content {
            width: 60%;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 46px;
            color: #666;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #666;
        }
        p1 {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: rgb(196, 196, 196);
        }
        .image img {
            width: 90%;
            border-radius: 2px;
        }
        h3 {
            color: #3a3a3a;
        }
        .links {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            height: 50%;
            gap: 20px;
            background-color: #0056A8;
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 50px;
            border-radius:2px ;
        }
      
        .links a {
            display: block;
            color: whitesmoke;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .links a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .dropdown-content {
            display: none;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color:#0056A8 ;
            border-left: 3px solid#f4f4f4;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .show {
            display: block;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <div class="content">
        <h1>Student Hubs</h1>
        <p>Visit us for help and advice on any aspect of your studies and life at the University of Auckland.</p>
        <div class="image">
            <img src="./public/css/images/image11.jpg" alt="Student Hub Image">
            <p>The Student Hubs are your physical gateway to Waipapa Taumata Rau | the University of Auckland. Our friendly staff are here to provide you with advice on any aspect of your studies and life at University.  </p>
        </div>
    </div>
<div class="links">
  <div>
    <h3 style="color: whitesmoke;">Related Links</h3><hr>
    <a href="#" onclick="toggleDropdown('itHub')">Student IT Hub</a>
    <div class="dropdown-content" id="itHub">
      <p1><strong>Announcements and News:</strong> Keep students updated with the latest news, events, and announcements related to the IT department.</p>
      <p1><strong>Resource Library:</strong> Access study materials, tutorials, and e-books.</p>
      <p1><strong>Job and Internship Listings:</strong> Find internship and job opportunities.</p>
      <p1><strong>Project Showcases:</strong> Highlight student projects and research.</p>
      <p1><strong>Discussion Forums:</strong> Engage in discussions and share knowledge.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div>
    <a href="#" onclick="toggleDropdown('libraries')">Libraries and Learning Services</a>
    <div class="dropdown-content" id="libraries">
      <p1><strong>Online Catalog:</strong> Search for books, journals, and other resources.</p>
      <p1><strong>E-Books and Journals:</strong> Access e-books and journals remotely.</p>
      <p1><strong>Research Databases:</strong> List available research databases.</p>
      <p1><strong>Study Spaces:</strong> Information about available study spaces.</p>
      <p1><strong>Academic Support Services:</strong> Tutoring and writing centers.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div>
    <a href="#" onclick="toggleDropdown('studyRoom')">Book a Group Study Room</a>
    <div class="dropdown-content" id="studyRoom">
      <p1><strong>Booking Policies:</strong> Maximum booking times and rules for usage.</p>
      <p1><strong>Instructions for Use:</strong> Step-by-step guide for booking rooms.</p>
      <p1><strong>Contact Information:</strong> Support details for booking issues.</p>
      <p1><strong>Feedback Form:</strong> Submit feedback on study room experiences.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="container2">
    <h2>Student Hubs services</h2>
    <hr />
    <p>
      Whether you are a prospective student or a current student from any of our faculties,
      we can help you with a wide range of information and services, including:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Exploring your study options with the University, including career pathways and Postgraduate level possibilities.</li>
      <li>Understanding and navigating entry into the University, including support with your application, admission, and enrolment.</li>
      <li>Course selection, enrolment, degree planning, and structuring your studies.</li>
      <li>Help and advice with fees, transcripts, and visa enquiries.</li>
      <li>Understanding and navigating University life.</li>
      <li>Library services and student IT support.</li>
      <li>University support options, including connection to wellbeing, disability, and engagement services.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Locations and hours</h3>
    <hr />
    <p>
      <strong>Student Hub, City Campus</strong><br />
      Te Herenga Mātauranga Whānui | General Library<br />
      Building 109, 5 Alfred Street, Auckland<br />
      <div>
        <a href="#" onclick="toggleDropdown('Wayfinding Map')">Wayfinding Map</a>
        <div class="dropdown-content" style="background-color: whitesmoke; border-left: 3px solid#0056A8;" id="Wayfinding Map">
            <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQDb6YW8G6HDbtCTMT5aIunIoOTpy488aR91g&s" alt="Wayfinding Map">
            <p>Main Entrance: Welcomes you with a spacious lobby and information desk.</p>
               <p> Library: A quiet space for study and research, equipped with computers and a vast collection of books.</p>
                <p>Cafeteria: Offers a variety of meals and snacks, with seating areas for relaxation and socializing.</p>
               <p> Classrooms: Multiple classrooms for lectures and seminars.</p>
               <p>Restrooms: Located near the main entrance and cafeteria.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </p>

    <h3>Visit To Campus</h3>
    <hr />
    <p>
        If you would like to speak with someone from our friendly team, or access any of our services, <br>
        please drop into one of our locations during our contact hours. Our closedown periods for<br>
        each of our Student Hub locations are mentioned above.
    <br><br>
        You do not need an appointment, simply visit any Hub during our opening hours and the team will be happy to help. 
    </p>
</div>
<script>
    function toggleDropdown(id) {
      const content = document.getElementById(id);
      content.classList.toggle("show");
    }
</script>
</body>
</html>